# Documentation-first workflow

## Before major decisions or rewrites

- Skim **README** (if present) and any notes in the repo root
- Check **`documents/`** session logs when continuing prior work
- Inspect the relevant **components** and **`src/content/`** files rather than guessing structure

## Rules

- Do not assume unfinished work without looking at the current tree
- Prefer existing patterns in `src/components/arc/` over inventing new architecture ad hoc
